<section><title>Geomajas purpose</title>
<para>
Geomajas is an Open source Web mapping software framework enabling 'real integrated GIS via the browser'.
</para><para>
Geomajas includes:
	</para>
	<itemizedlist>
		<listitem><para>Geometry and attribute editing with snapping support.</para></listitem>
		<listitem><para>Complex attribute and relation mapping (one-to-many, many-to-one), helping you implement business logic.</para></listitem>
		<listitem><para>Advanced querying capabilities (searching, filters, styles, ...)</para></listitem>
	</itemizedlist>

</section>
